OL,3,C'Just get on with it!' Government
OL,4,Curged to act on medical scandal
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FIt's been a year since England's
OL,8,FPatient Safety Commissioner set out
OL,9,Fplans for an compensation scheme for
OL,10,Fpeople affected by two of the biggest
OL,11,Fmedical scandals in recent history.
OL,13,FSo far, no payments have been made.
OL,15,F"My message to the Government a year
OL,16,Fago was 'Get on with it', and although
OL,17,Fthe Government has changed, my message
OL,18,Fremains the same", Professor Henrietta
OL,19,FHughes told ITV News.
