OL,3,C'Just get on with it!' Government
OL,4,Curged to act on medical scandal
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"Waiting for redress doesn't put the
OL,8,Fsuffering of those who have been
OL,9,Fharmed on pause, they need help right
OL,10,Fnow."
OL,12,FThe Hughes Report - published on the 7
OL,13,FFebruary 2024 - examined the impact of
OL,14,Ftwo medical controversies: the
OL,15,Fepilepsy medication Sodium Valproate,
OL,16,Fand the use of pelvic mesh.
