OL,3,C'Just get on with it!' Government
OL,4,Curged to act on medical scandal
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FThe findings of the Hughes Report were
OL,8,Fclear: a compensation scheme for
OL,9,Fpeople affected by pelvic mesh or
OL,10,Fsodium valproate was "urgently
OL,11,Fneeded", with the Patient Safety
OL,12,FCommissioner recommending interim
OL,13,Fpayments for all patients, followed by
OL,14,Fa main scheme with pay outs based on
OL,15,Fthe needs of each individual.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
