OL,3,C'Just get on with it!' Government
OL,4,Curged to act on medical scandal
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"Justice delayed is justice denied -
OL,8,Fand the patients who have been harmed
OL,9,Fare still experiencing pain, they have
OL,10,Fproblems with mobility, they have
OL,11,Fphysical disabilities and learning
OL,12,Fdisabilities. They need equipment,
OL,13,Fthey need support, they need the right
OL,14,Fkind of assessments, and all of these
OL,15,Fthings are not available to them
OL,16,Fwithout the right kind of redress"
