OL,3,C'Just get on with it!' Government
OL,4,Curged to act on medical scandal
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,FProfessor Henrietta Hughes spoke to
OL,8,FPolitical Correspondent Lise McNally
OL,9,Fto mark the anniversary of her report,
OL,10,Fsharing why there is still the need
OL,11,Ffor urgent action, and how she feels
OL,12,Fabout the delay in implementing her
OL,13,Frecommendations:
OL,15,F"Theres a big difference between warm
OL,16,Fwords to patients and money landing in
OL,17,Ftheir accounts. And I think the
OL,18,FGovernment and the previous Government
OL,19,Fhave both struggled with how to square
OL,20,Fthat."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
