OL,3,C'Just get on with it!' Government
OL,4,Curged to act on medical scandal
OL,5,Ccompensation
OL,7,F"They can clearly see the suffering,
OL,8,Fthey can clearly see the case for
OL,9,Fredress, but there's also a practical
OL,10,Faspect to this which is how to turn
OL,11,Fthat into a sensible plan. Now, I've
OL,12,Fpublished a sensible plan, I would
OL,13,Fdirect them to the options I've set
OL,14,Fout"
OL,16,FITV News asked the Government for an
OL,17,Fupdate on when the interim payments or
OL,18,Fthe full compensation scheme would be
OL,19,Fimplemented.
